==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*παραδειγματίζω / paradeigmatizō / par-ad-igue-mat-id'-zo
*From [[παρά]] {{GG|3844}} and [[δειγματίζω]] {{GG|1165}}; to show alongside (the public), that is, expose to infamy: 

===Verb===
'''παραδειγματίζω'''

# make a public [[example]], put to an open [[shame]].

